{#- Expects: ticker (str), message (str)

    Sub-task 5.3 (spec §3.5.4 R1-Major-2) — 404 fragment when the requested
    ticker has no candidate row in the latest completed pipeline run, or
    when sizing parameters are degenerate. Rendered as a <tr> so HTMX
    can swap into the original <tbody>; the row-target prefix guard in
    `swing/web/app.py:_ROW_TARGET_PREFIXES` ensures any 4xx/5xx along the
    way also produces <tr>-rooted markup. -#}
<tr id="hyp-rec-row-{{ ticker }}" class="expand-unavailable">
  <td colspan="9">
    <span>{{ message }}</span>
    <button hx-get="/hyp-recs/refresh"
            hx-target="#hypothesis-recommendations"
            hx-swap="outerHTML"
            hx-headers='{"HX-Request": "true"}'>Close</button>
  </td>
</tr>
